column16: Greg Dobbs lines out softly to left fielder Jason Kubel.
Giancarlo Stanton singles on a ground ball to left fielder Jason Kubel.   Gorkys Hernandez scores.    Jose Reyes to 2nd.
Carlos Lee lines out to center fielder Chris Young.   Gorkys Hernandez to 3rd.
Sam Demel intentionally walks Jose Reyes.
Bryan Petersen out on a sacrifice bunt to pitcher Sam Demel.   Gorkys Hernandez to 2nd.
Gorkys Hernandez singles on a ground ball to shortstop Jake Elmore.
